Develop a strategy and roadmap for advanced analytics within the operating divisions that aligns with Deltas digital transformation goals of improving operations reliability, customer service, employee satisfaction, and financial performance
 Lead Delta business units to optimize operational decision making through the deployment of predictive analytics and machine learning
 Align and lead team in the implementation of decision science products for the operations divisions, including the use of reinforcement learning and artificial intelligence
 Guide business problem identification utilizing advanced quantitative methods to influence decisions and identify opportunities to bring value to customers and the operation
 Support operational leaders with scientific insights throughout major airline operational disruption including planning, execution, and post-event analysis
 Responsible for developing and driving short and long-term data strategy for the Operations divisions, and liaise with IT to improve integrity and availability of data
 Drive consistency and improvement in the visualization of data, including cross-divisional dashboards
 Communicate information and insights strategy, and results to senior leaders and cross-divisional partners
 Establish expectations and priorities, drive performance, coach, develop and mentor team, and create a positive, dynamic and collaborative work environment
